7cbb38df40a6e3a312698b37a073ee252518937e6144b78729f74264634c077b3b804afe6e7f13be8041217d036794b71973076f4830f86f796b8920cd5e0fb0  0001-qqc2-desktop-style-Menu-make-sure-implicitWidth-height-is-never-0.patch
"
